  <phrase title="braintree_api_keys_explain" version_id="2021470" version_string="2.2.14"><![CDATA[<a href="https://www.braintreegateway.com/" target="_blank">Braintree Hesabınızdaki</a> Account > My User > API Keys, Tokenization Keys, Encryption Keys > View Authorizations sayfasındaki API anahtarlarını ve Merchant ID'yi girin.<br />
